 />\n朗拿度回憶說：「原本我已經續約，之後打算飛去巴西國家隊報到。只是5日後，巴塞告訴我不能續約了，一切決定權都不在我手中，其實我是想留隊的。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7iTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=053406c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"d5a12dbd615a7167421fd3ba12f837e896280684","tid":2183287,"uid":72085,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b78196448479f5f59766b617e81ed2b250556e4c","tid":2183287,"uid":10757,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T00:42:14.000Z","msg":"接下來似乎只有一條路可走：對簿公堂，就違約金條款是否有效打官司。巴塞前主席們已在炮轟美斯不忠誠，球迷也開始分裂，由幾天前全力支持美斯，變為現在出現聲音懷疑美斯對巴塞的愛。看來，好合好散已不可能，雙方要撕破臉滿身是傷的分手。<br />\n<br />\n疤狗PR勁撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港政府有冇諗著搵佢地搞宣傳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:07:59.000Z","msg":"諗多左，根本唔會有球迷企球會嗰邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老細係咩人品，係人都知，仲要換完教練開完會人地先話走，邊個搞事先好清楚啦"},{"pid":"3e9689dc8cb2cae55915790498b8264188f26c98","tid":2183287,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:11:09.000Z","msg":"美帝 鐘意去邊就去邊<br />\n再嘈好似Bale咁罷踢"},{"pid":"899426c567135fc63ce70ce133b8413746807d79","tid":2183287,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:44:46.000Z","msg":"費高呢"},{"pid":"0a2a7033731a638831fab0436db1024cb52d0d9d","tid":2183287,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"899426c567135fc63ce70ce133b8413746807d79","tid":2183287,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:44:46.000Z","msg":"費高呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:14:25.000Z","msg":"佢自己走？"},{"pid":"9192c58b5054ec1ad1321dbda51c57e8d39eb598","tid":2183287,"uid":261873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0a2a7033731a638831fab0436db1024cb52d0d9d","tid":2183287,"uid":1